<h1>Thank You for Your Request!</h1>

<p>Hi {{customerFirstName}},</p>

<p>
    We've received your {{serviceCategory}} service request and our team is reviewing it now.
    You'll hear from us within <strong>24 hours</strong> with a detailed quote.
</p>

<div class="info-box">
    <h3>Your Request Summary</h3>
    <p><strong>Reference Number:</strong> {{referenceNumber}}</p>
    <p><strong>Service Type:</strong> {{capitalize serviceCategory}}</p>
    <p><strong>Service Needed:</strong> {{capitalize serviceType}}</p>
    {{#if urgency}}
    <p><strong>Urgency:</strong> {{capitalize urgency}}</p>
    {{/if}}
    <p><strong>Submitted:</strong> {{formatDate submittedAt "long"}}</p>
</div>

{{#if description}}
<h2>Service Details</h2>
<p>{{description}}</p>
{{/if}}

<h2>What Happens Next?</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Step 1:</strong> Our team reviews your request (within 2 hours)</li>
    <li><strong>Step 2:</strong> We prepare a detailed quote with pricing (within 24 hours)</li>
    <li><strong>Step 3:</strong> You receive an email with your quote and acceptance link</li>
    <li><strong>Step 4:</strong> Once accepted, you can schedule your appointment online</li>
</ul>

<div class="info-box" style="background-color: #fef3c7; border-left-color: #f59e0b;">
    <h3>Need Immediate Assistance?</h3>
    <p>
        {{#if_eq urgency "EMERGENCY"}}
        For emergency services, please call us directly at <strong>{{organizationPhone}}</strong>
        {{else}}
        If you have questions, feel free to reach out:
        <br>
        Phone: <strong>{{organizationPhone}}</strong>
        <br>
        Email: <strong>{{organizationEmail}}</strong>
        {{/if_eq}}
    </p>
</div>

<p>
    We appreciate your business and look forward to serving you!
</p>

<p>
    Best regards,<br>
    <strong>The {{organizationName}} Team</strong>
</p>